0E456506.Line20.5421B: If you would kill the cannibals, it would ease both of our spirits.

89D5762F.Line18.5421D: I've had enough rest to last a lifetime! I can stand -- (cries)

C1C4CEDD.Line9.5421B: (sigh) The cannibals maimed him. Ancestors were watching over him because the others were unrecognizable. I await the day I can avenge them two-fold, but the living takes precedence.
